</code></pre></p> </li> <li> <p>The extract stage automatically routes <code>.md</code>, <code>.html</code>, and <code>.docx</code> through their respective extractors:</p> </li> <li><code>MdPandocExtractor</code></li> <li><code>HtmlPandocExtractor</code></li> <li><code>DocxPandocExtractor</code></li> </ol>
